Description:
Also, while you didn't ask, I'm taking the liberty of offering some suggestions for your trip to the Rockies - I've done them all (more than once) and they are totally worthy and fabulous - I can't imagine doing the Rockies without these: 
* Moraine Lake (near Lake Louise) 
* Columbia Icefields; 
* Johnston Canyon (Banff); 
* Canmore - helicopter tour (through the 3 Sisters 

Banff:  Gondola to top
